World’s 1st Molded LW Type 2 Kit🥇
Self Made Hot Wheel🏎
I’m FAST AF 💨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by GUAC ZILLA in Race Service with @michelinusa, @ms.emelia, @tannerfox, @officialcainvelasquez, @thestradman, and @codybwalker. May be an image of 12 people, people standing and outerwear.

node.text:
@michelinusa x @thegranturismo #MichelinGTSport #RaceforGood was EPIC. @tannerfox smashes initial top four but then spun out 😐. Still a huge win for @reachoutww and @codybwalker taking home 20K for a GREAT cause. 
———
Special thanks to @michelinusa & @lewlew_lemans for making the BEST tires on the planet. 
———
Can I get into @thegranturismo I’m fast tooo?? 🏎💨

node.text:
Vote and help me win $20,000 for March of Dimes.  16 influencers will be battling on Gran Turismo Sport for the “Michelin + Gran Turismo Race For Good” livestream challenge, with the winner receiving a check to the charity of their choice. Watch the livestream race at 5PM PT on 11/18.

The driver with the most votes will race on the stickiest Michelin tires during the first round of competition, giving them a performance advantage. Vote for me and enter for a chance to win cool prizes at michelinman.com/granturismo
——
VOTE FOR @tannerfox LINK IN BIO!
——
#MICHELINGTSPORT
#RACEFORGOOD
